            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">Insanas</supplied> lites odiosaque iurgia differ <lb n="2"/>si potes aut gressus ad tua tecta refer <lb n="3"/>lascivos voltus et blandos aufer ocellos <lb n="4"/>coniuge ab alterius sit tibi in ore pudor <lb n="5"/>abluat unda pedes puer et detergeat udos <lb n="6"/>mappa torum velet lintea nostra cave
            </ab></div>
